# ENTITY::HAS_ENTITY_BEEN_DAMAGED_BY_ANY_OBJECT

## Summary
Returns TRUE if the last thing to damage the entity was an object

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity

## Returns
* **BOOL**
